                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12332224" author="stoney" created="Mon, 17 Oct 2005 22:08:31 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Here is a patch that solves the problem. The FieldsReader now looks at FieldInfo.storeOffsetWithTermVector and FieldInfo.storePositionWithTermVector and creates the Field with the correct TermVector parameter.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12332492" author="bmesser" created="Thu, 20 Oct 2005 03:02:55 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Frank,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;thanks for the patch. I&apos;ve reviewed it and commited it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Bernhard&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
